{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775847410247,"sessionID":"ses_287408d25ffeY2qCjqVxnnpeMt","part":{"id":"prt_d78c10900001TvUrHlw4NRb0Xc","messageID":"msg_d78bfea36001w32EaeGbwODnk1","sessionID":"ses_287408d25ffeY2qCjqVxnnpeMt","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-a08b5f29f0134239819f260167306319","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-008 — Sandbox GC 定时清理机制\n\n**Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`\n**Language:** Go\n**Size:** S\n\n## 垃圾回收核心结构\n\n### 场景: 定义 GarbageCollector 结构体\n\n**GIVEN** 需要定时清理空闲和过期的 Sandbox 资源\n**WHEN** 定义垃圾回收器核心结构体\n**THEN** 创建 `garbage_collector.go` 文件，定义 `GarbageCollector` 结构体\n\n```go\ntype GarbageCollector struct {\n    dynamicClient dynamic.Interface\n    storeClient   store.Store\n    interval      time.Duration\n    ctx           context.Context\n    cancel        context.CancelFunc\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 定义 Sandbox 资源 GVR\n\n**GIVEN** 需要操作 Kubernetes 的 Sandbox 和 SandboxClaim 资源\n**WHEN** 定义资源 GroupVersionResource\n**THEN** 声明 Sandbox 和 SandboxClaim 的 GVR 常量\n\n```go\nvar (\n    SandboxGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n        Group:    \"agents.x-k8s.io\",\n        Version:  \"v1alpha1\",\n        Resource: \"sandboxes\",\n    }\n\n    SandboxClaimGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n        Group:    \"extensions.agents.x-k8s.io\",\n        Version:  \"v1alpha1\",\n        Resource: \"sandboxclaims\",\n    }\n)\n```\n\n## 清理原因类型定义\n\n### 场景: 定义 Sandbox 清理原因\n\n**GIVEN** 需要区分不同的 Sandbox 清理场景\n**WHEN** 定义清理原因枚举类型\n**THEN** 在 `types/sandbox_types.go` 中定义 `SandboxCleanupReason` 类型\n\n```go\ntype SandboxCleanupReason string\n\nconst (\n    CleanupReasonManual      SandboxCleanupReason = \"manual\"\n    CleanupReasonIdleTimeout SandboxCleanupReason = \"idle_timeout\"\n    CleanupReasonExpired     SandboxCleanupReason = \"expired\"\n)\n```\n\n### 场景: 定义清理审计日志条目\n\n**GIVEN** 需要记录 Sandbox 清理操作的审计信息\n**WHEN** 定义审计日志条目结构\n**THEN** 在 `types/sandbox_types.go` 中定义 `CleanupAuditEntry` 结构\n\n```go\ntype CleanupAuditEntry struct {\n    SessionID    string               `json:\"sessionId\"`\n    SandboxID    string               `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n    Namespace    string               `json:\"namespace\"`\n    Reason       SandboxCleanupReason `json:\"reason\"`\n    DeletedAt    time.Time            `json:\"deletedAt\"`\n    Success      bool                 `json:\"success\"`\n    ErrorMessage string               `json:\"errorMessage,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n## 垃圾回收器初始化\n\n### 场景: 创建垃圾回收器实例\n\n**GIVEN** 已有 dynamic client 和 store client\n**WHEN** 创建垃圾回收器实例\n**THEN** 初始化所有字段并创建可取消的 context\n\n```go\nfunc NewGarbageCollector(\n    dynamicClient dynamic.Interface,\n    storeClient store.Store,\n    interval time.Duration,\n) *GarbageCollector {\n    ctx, cancel := context.WithCancel(context.Background())\n    return &GarbageCollector{\n        dynamicClient: dynamicClient,\n        storeClient:   storeClient,\n        interval:      interval,\n        ctx:           ctx,\n        cancel:        cancel,\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## 生命周期管理\n\n### 场景: 启动垃圾回收器\n\n**GIVEN** 垃圾回收器实例已创建\n**WHEN** 调用 Start 方法\n**THEN** 启动独立的 goroutine 运行 GC 循环\n\n```go\nfunc (gc *GarbageCollector) Start() {\n    go gc.gcLoop()\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 停止垃圾回收器\n\n**GIVEN** 垃圾回收器正在运行\n**WHEN** 调用 Stop 方法\n**THEN** 取消 context，优雅停止 GC 循环\n\n```go\nfunc (gc *GarbageCollector) Stop() {\n    gc.cancel()\n}\n```\n\n## GC 循环机制\n\n### 场景: 实现 GC 循环\n\n**GIVEN** 垃圾回收器已启动\n**WHEN** GC 循环运行\n**THEN** 定时执行 tick 方法，直到 context 被取消\n\n```go\nfunc (gc *GarbageCollector) gcLoop() {\n    ticker := time.NewTicker(gc.interval)\n    defer ticker.Stop()\n\n    klog.Info(\"GarbageCollector started\")\n\n    for {\n        select {\n        case <-gc.ctx.Done():\n            klog.Info(\"GarbageCollector stopped\")\n            return\n        case <-ticker.C:\n            gc.tick()\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 设置单次 tick 超时\n\n**GIVEN** 单次 tick 可能耗时较长\n**WHEN** 执行 tick 方法\n**THEN** 为单次 tick 设置超时上下文，防止阻塞\n\n```go\nfunc (gc *GarbageCollector) tick() {\n    tickCtx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(gc.ctx, GCSingleTickTimeout)\n    defer cancel()\n\n    now := time.Now()\n    idleThreshold := now.Add(-DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout)\n    expiredThreshold := now\n\n    idleSandboxes, err := gc.storeClient.ListInactiveSandboxes(tickCtx, idleThreshold, 16)\n    if err != nil {\n        klog.Errorf(\"Failed to list inactive sandboxes: %v\", err)\n    } else {\n        for _, sandbox := range idleSandboxes {\n            gc.deleteSandbox(tickCtx, sandbox, wmTypes.CleanupReasonIdleTimeout)\n        }\n    }\n\n    expiredSandboxes, err := gc.storeClient.ListExpiredSandboxes(tickCtx, expiredThreshold, 16)\n    if err != nil {\n        klog.Errorf(\"Failed to list expired sandboxes: %v\", err)\n    } else {\n        for _, sandbox := range expiredSandboxes {\n            gc.deleteSandbox(tickCtx, sandbox, wmTypes.CleanupReasonExpired)\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## 空闲 Sandbox 清理\n\n### 场景: 查询空闲 Sandbox\n\n**GIVEN** 当前时间为 `now`\n**WHEN** 查询空闲超时的 Sandbox\n**THEN** 计算空闲阈值并从 store 查询\n\n```go\nnow := time.Now()\nidleThreshold := now.Add(-DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout)\n\nidleSandboxes, err := gc.storeClient.ListInactiveSandboxes(tickCtx, idleThreshold, 16)\n```\n\n### 场景: 清理空闲 Sandbox\n\n**GIVEN** 查询到空闲的 Sandbox 列表\n**WHEN** 遍历空闲 Sandbox 列表\n**THEN** 对每个空闲 Sandbox 调用删除方法，原因为 `CleanupReasonIdleTimeout`\n\n```go\nfor _, sandbox := range idleSandboxes {\n    gc.deleteSandbox(tickCtx, sandbox, wmTypes.CleanupReasonIdleTimeout)\n}\n```\n\n## 过期 Sandbox 清理\n\n### 场景: 查询过期 Sandbox\n\n**GIVEN** 当前时间为 `now`\n**WHEN** 查询过期的 Sandbox\n**THEN** 使用当前时间作为阈值从 store 查询\n\n```go\nnow := time.Now()\nexpiredThreshold := now\n\nexpiredSandboxes, err := gc.storeClient.ListExpiredSandboxes(tickCtx, expiredThreshold, 16)\n```\n\n### 场景: 清理过期 Sandbox\n\n**GIVEN** 查询到过期的 Sandbox 列表\n**WHEN** 遍历过期 Sandbox 列表\n**THEN** 对每个过期 Sandbox 调用删除方法，原因为 `CleanupReasonExpired`\n\n```go\nfor _, sandbox := range expiredSandboxes {\n    gc.deleteSandbox(tickCtx, sandbox, wmTypes.CleanupReasonExpired)\n}\n```\n\n## Sandbox 删除\n\n### 场景: 选择正确的 GVR\n\n**GIVEN** Sandbox 信息包含 Kind 字段\n**WHEN** 删除 Sandbox\n**THEN** 根据 Kind 选择正确的 GVR（Sandbox 或 SandboxClaim）\n\n```go\ngvr := SandboxGVR\nif sandbox.Kind == \"SandboxClaim\" {\n    gvr = SandboxClaimGVR\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 设置删除操作超时\n\n**GIVEN** 需要删除 Sandbox 资源\n**WHEN** 调用 Kubernetes API 删除\n**THEN** 为删除操作设置独立的超时上下文\n\n```go\ndeleteCtx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(ctx, DeleteTimeout)\ndefer cancel()\n```\n\n### 场景: 删除 Sandbox 资源\n\n**GIVEN** 已确定正确的 GVR 和 namespace\n**WHEN** 调用 Kubernetes API 删除\n**THEN** 使用 dynamic client 删除资源\n\n```go\nerr := gc.dynamicClient.Resource(gvr).\n    Namespace(sandbox.SandboxNamespace).\n    Delete(deleteCtx, sandbox.SandboxID, metav1.DeleteOptions{})\n```\n\n### 场景: 处理删除成功\n\n**GIVEN** Kubernetes API 删除成功或资源不存在\n**WHEN** 删除操作完成\n**THEN** 从 store 中删除记录，标记审计为成功\n\n```go\nif err := gc.storeClient.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sandbox.SessionID); err != nil {\n    klog.Warningf(\"Failed to delete sandbox %s from store: %v\", sandbox.SessionID, err)\n}\nauditEntry.Success = true\nklog.Infof(\"Deleted sandbox %s/%s (reason: %s)\", sandbox.SandboxNamespace, sandbox.SandboxID, reason)\n```\n\n### 场景: 处理删除失败\n\n**GIVEN** Kubernetes API 删除失败且不是 NotFound 错误\n**WHEN** 删除操作失败\n**THEN** 记录错误信息到审计，标记审计为失败\n\n```go\nif err != nil && !apierrors.IsNotFound(err) {\n    auditEntry.ErrorMessage = err.Error()\n    auditEntry.Success = false\n    klog.Errorf(\"Failed to delete sandbox %s/%s: %v\", sandbox.SandboxNamespace, sandbox.SandboxID, err)\n}\n```\n\n## 审计日志\n\n### 场景: 创建审计条目\n\n**GIVEN** 准备删除 Sandbox\n**WHEN** 创建审计日志条目\n**THEN** 记录所有关键信息\n\n```go\nauditEntry := &wmTypes.CleanupAuditEntry{\n    SessionID: sandbox.SessionID,\n    SandboxID: sandbox.SandboxID,\n    Namespace: sandbox.SandboxNamespace,\n    Reason:    reason,\n    DeletedAt: time.Now(),\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 记录审计日志\n\n**GIVEN** 删除操作完成\n**WHEN** 记录审计日志\n**THEN** 输出结构化的审计信息\n\n```go\nfunc (gc *GarbageCollector) recordAudit(entry *wmTypes.CleanupAuditEntry) {\n    klog.Infof(\"Cleanup audit: sessionId=%s sandboxId=%s namespace=%s reason=%s success=%v deletedAt=%s\",\n        entry.SessionID, entry.SandboxID, entry.Namespace, entry.Reason, entry.Success, entry.DeletedAt.Format(time.RFC3339))\n    if entry.ErrorMessage != \"\" {\n        klog.Infof(\"Cleanup audit error: %s\", entry.ErrorMessage)\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## 错误处理\n\n### 场景: 处理查询空闲 Sandbox 错误\n\n**GIVEN** 查询空闲 Sandbox 时发生错误\n**WHEN** 捕获错误\n**THEN** 记录错误日志，继续执行过期 Sandbox 查询\n\n```go\nidleSandboxes, err := gc.storeClient.ListInactiveSandboxes(tickCtx, idleThreshold, 16)\nif err != nil {\n    klog.Errorf(\"Failed to list inactive sandboxes: %v\", err)\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 处理查询过期 Sandbox 错误\n\n**GIVEN** 查询过期 Sandbox 时发生错误\n**WHEN** 捕获错误\n**THEN** 记录错误日志\n\n```go\nexpiredSandboxes, err := gc.storeClient.ListExpiredSandboxes(tickCtx, expiredThreshold, 16)\nif err != nil {\n    klog.Errorf(\"Failed to list expired sandboxes: %v\", err)\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 处理 Store 删除失败\n\n**GIVEN** Kubernetes 删除成功但 Store 删除失败\n**WHEN** Store 删除失败\n**THEN** 记录警告日志，不影响整体流程\n\n```go\nif err := gc.storeClient.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sandbox.SessionID); err != nil {\n    klog.Warningf(\"Failed to delete sandbox %s from store: %v\", sandbox.SessionID, err)\n}\n```\n\n## 配置常量\n\n### 场景: 定义 GC 间隔\n\n**GIVEN** 需要配置 GC 检查频率\n**WHEN** 定义 GC 间隔常量\n**THEN** 在 `defaults.go` 中设置合理的默认值\n\n```go\nconst (\n    GCInterval = 15 * time.Second\n)\n```\n\n### 场景: 定义空闲超时\n\n**GIVEN** 需要配置 Sandbox 空闲超时时间\n**WHEN** 定义空闲超时常量\n**THEN** 在 `defaults.go` 中设置默认值\n\n```go\nconst (\n    DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n)\n```\n\n### 场景: 定义超时配置\n\n**GIVEN** 需要配置各操作的超时时间\n**WHEN** 定义超时常量\n**THEN** 在 `defaults.go` 中设置合理的超时值\n\n```go\nconst (\n    GCSingleTickTimeout = 2 * time.Minute\n    DeleteTimeout       = 30 * time.Second\n)\n```\n\n## 测试场景\n\n### 场景: 测试空闲 Sandbox 清理\n\n**GIVEN** 使用 fake store 和 fake dynamic client\n**WHEN** 测试 tick 方法清理空闲 Sandbox\n**THEN** 验证调用了正确的 store 方法和删除操作\n\n```go\nfunc TestGarbageCollector_Tick_IdleSandboxes(t *testing.T) {\n    mockStore := &mockStoreForGC{}\n    idleSandboxes := []*types.SandboxInfo{\n        {\n            SessionID:        \"idle-session-1\",\n            SandboxID:        \"idle-sandbox-1\",\n            SandboxNamespace: \"default\",\n            Kind:             \"Sandbox\",\n        },\n    }\n    mockStore.On(\"ListInactiveSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return(idleSandboxes, nil)\n    mockStore.On(\"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, \"idle-session-1\").Return(nil)\n    mockStore.On(\"ListExpiredSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return([]*types.SandboxInfo{}, nil)\n\n    scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n    fakeDynamicClient := fake.NewSimpleDynamicClient(scheme)\n\n    gc := NewGarbageCollector(fakeDynamicClient, mockStore, GCInterval)\n\n    gc.tick()\n\n    mockStore.AssertCalled(t, \"ListInactiveSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16)\n    mockStore.AssertCalled(t, \"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, \"idle-session-1\")\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 测试过期 Sandbox 清理\n\n**GIVEN** 使用 fake store 和 fake dynamic client\n**WHEN** 测试 tick 方法清理过期 Sandbox\n**THEN** 验证调用了正确的 store 方法和删除操作\n\n```go\nfunc TestGarbageCollector_Tick_ExpiredSandboxes(t *testing.T) {\n    mockStore := &mockStoreForGC{}\n    expiredSandboxes := []*types.SandboxInfo{\n        {\n            SessionID:        \"expired-session-1\",\n            SandboxID:        \"expired-sandbox-1\",\n            SandboxNamespace: \"default\",\n            Kind:             \"Sandbox\",\n        },\n    }\n    mockStore.On(\"ListExpiredSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return(expiredSandboxes, nil)\n    mockStore.On(\"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, \"expired-session-1\").Return(nil)\n    mockStore.On(\"ListInactiveSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return([]*types.SandboxInfo{}, nil)\n\n    scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n    fakeDynamicClient := fake.NewSimpleDynamicClient(scheme)\n\n    gc := NewGarbageCollector(fakeDynamicClient, mockStore, GCInterval)\n\n    gc.tick()\n\n    mockStore.AssertCalled(t, \"ListExpiredSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16)\n    mockStore.AssertCalled(t, \"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, \"expired-session-1\")\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 测试 Kubernetes NotFound 处理\n\n**GIVEN** Sandbox 在 Kubernetes 中已不存在\n**WHEN** GC 尝试删除该 Sandbox\n**THEN** 仍然从 store 中删除记录，不报错\n\n```go\nfunc TestGarbageCollector_Tick_KubernetesNotFound(t *testing.T) {\n    mockStore := &mockStoreForGC{}\n    sandboxInfo := &types.SandboxInfo{\n        SessionID:        \"missing-session\",\n        SandboxID:        \"missing-sandbox\",\n        SandboxNamespace: \"default\",\n        Kind:             \"Sandbox\",\n    }\n    mockStore.On(\"ListInactiveSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return([]*types.SandboxInfo{sandboxInfo}, nil)\n    mockStore.On(\"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, \"missing-session\").Return(nil)\n    mockStore.On(\"ListExpiredSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return([]*types.SandboxInfo{}, nil)\n\n    scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n    fakeDynamicClient := fake.NewSimpleDynamicClient(scheme)\n\n    gc := NewGarbageCollector(fakeDynamicClient, mockStore, GCInterval)\n\n    gc.tick()\n\n    mockStore.AssertCalled(t, \"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, \"missing-session\")\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 测试 GC 启动停止\n\n**GIVEN** 垃圾回收器实例已创建\n**WHEN** 启动 GC 并等待几次 tick 后停止\n**THEN** GC 能正常启动和停止，无 panic\n\n```go\nfunc TestGarbageCollector_StartStop(t *testing.T) {\n    mockStore := &mockStoreForGC{}\n    mockStore.On(\"ListInactiveSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return([]*types.SandboxInfo{}, nil)\n    mockStore.On(\"ListExpiredSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return([]*types.SandboxInfo{}, nil)\n\n    scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n    fakeDynamicClient := fake.NewSimpleDynamicClient(scheme)\n\n    gc := NewGarbageCollector(fakeDynamicClient, mockStore, 100*time.Millisecond)\n\n    gc.Start()\n\n    time.Sleep(250 * time.Millisecond)\n\n    gc.Stop()\n\n    time.Sleep(50 * time.Millisecond)\n    assert.True(t, true, \"GC stopped without panic\")\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 测试查询错误处理\n\n**GIVEN** Store 返回查询错误\n**WHEN** GC 执行 tick\n**THEN** 记录错误日志并继续执行\n\n```go\nfunc TestGarbageCollector_Tick_ListInactiveError(t *testing.T) {\n    mockStore := &mockStoreForGC{}\n    mockStore.On(\"ListInactiveSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return([]*types.SandboxInfo{}, assert.AnError)\n    mockStore.On(\"ListExpiredSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return([]*types.SandboxInfo{}, nil)\n\n    scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n    fakeDynamicClient := fake.NewSimpleDynamicClient(scheme)\n\n    gc := NewGarbageCollector(fakeDynamicClient, mockStore, GCInterval)\n\n    gc.tick()\n\n    mockStore.AssertCalled(t, \"ListInactiveSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16)\n    mockStore.AssertCalled(t, \"ListExpiredSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16)\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 测试同时清理空闲和过期 Sandbox\n\n**GIVEN** 同时存在空闲和过期的 Sandbox\n**WHEN** GC 执行 tick\n**THEN** 清理所有符合条件的 Sandbox\n\n```go\nfunc TestGarbageCollector_Tick_BothLists(t *testing.T) {\n    mockStore := &mockStoreForGC{}\n    idleSandboxes := []*types.SandboxInfo{\n        {\n            SessionID:        \"idle-session-1\",\n            SandboxID:        \"idle-sandbox-1\",\n            SandboxNamespace: \"default\",\n            Kind:             \"Sandbox\",\n        },\n    }\n    expiredSandboxes := []*types.SandboxInfo{\n        {\n            SessionID:        \"expired-session-1\",\n            SandboxID:        \"expired-sandbox-1\",\n            SandboxNamespace: \"default\",\n            Kind:             \"Sandbox\",\n        },\n    }\n    mockStore.On(\"ListInactiveSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return(idleSandboxes, nil)\n    mockStore.On(\"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, \"idle-session-1\").Return(nil)\n    mockStore.On(\"ListExpiredSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return(expiredSandboxes, nil)\n    mockStore.On(\"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, \"expired-session-1\").Return(nil)\n\n    scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n    fakeDynamicClient := fake.NewSimpleDynamicClient(scheme)\n\n    gc := NewGarbageCollector(fakeDynamicClient, mockStore, GCInterval)\n\n    gc.tick()\n\n    mockStore.AssertNumberOfCalls(t, \"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", 2)\n}\n```\n\n## 最终验证\n\n### 场景: 验证 GC 完整功能\n\n**GIVEN** 所有 GC 组件已实现\n**WHEN** 运行完整测试套件\n**THEN** 所有单元测试通过，GC 能够正确清理空闲和过期的 Sandbox\n\n### 场景: 验证 GC 性能\n\n**GIVEN** GC 已部署到生产环境\n**WHEN** 存在大量 Sandbox 需要清理\n**THEN** GC 能够稳定运行，单次 tick 在超时时间内完成\n\n### 场景: 验证审计日志完整性\n\n**GIVEN** GC 正在运行\n**WHEN** 清理 Sandbox\n**THEN** 所有清理操作都有完整的审计日志记录\n\n## 文件组织\n\n### 场景: 文件结构清晰分离\n\n**GIVEN** pkg/workloadmanager 模块需要组织 GC 代码\n**WHEN** 创建文件结构\n**THEN** 按职责分离文件：\n\n```\npkg/workloadmanager/\n├── garbage_collector.go       # GarbageCollector 核心实现\n├── garbage_collector_test.go  # 单元测试\n├── types/\n│   └── sandbox_types.go       # Sandbox 相关类型定义\n└── defaults.go                # 配置常量\n```","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/controller/reconciler/codeinterpreter.go\">\nERROR [63:7] undefined: statusConditionsEqual\nERROR [106:6] undefined: statusConditionsEqual\nERROR [173:2] declared and not used: logger\nERROR [242:5] undefined: podSpecsEqual\nERROR [267:29] undefined: convertEnvVars\nERROR [274:25] undefined: convertResources\nERROR [326:6] undefined: statusConditionsEqual\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T16312